# Files executed on Linux must keep LF endings even on Windows checkouts — a CRLF shebang
# breaks them inside the Docker build (Story 9 / ADR-008). gradlew's CRLF bit us once; it is
# additionally stripped in the Dockerfile as a backstop.
gradlew        text eol=lf
*.sh           text eol=lf
Dockerfile     text eol=lf
*.dockerfile   text eol=lf
.dockerignore  text eol=lf
